title: Emile Bernard Two Women on the Asnières Footbridge Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from Emile Bernard’s Two Women on the Asnières Footbridge, 1887, from the exhibit Van Gogh and the Avant-Garde: The Modern Landscape at The Art Institute of Chicago.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces.

  • Dimensions: 2.5 x 3.5 inches.
  • Single Magnet.
